   - A "complete" status is reached ONLY when all mandatory fields (gender, height, date_of_birth) are collected AND all optional fields (name, blood_type) have been either collected or explicitly asked once.
   - If any mandatory field is missing, OR if an optional field has not been asked yet, status MUST be "incomplete".
   - Document the status decision in "thoughts".

